00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:51,120
Zhan Yan, you're too rude to him.

296
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:52,720
I don't despise you.

297
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:54,880
Don't think too much.

298
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:56,420
I know.

299
00:21:56,420 --> 00:21:57,480
Take it easy.

300
00:21:57,480 --> 00:22:01,148
I'll take the minutes and send them to you.

301
00:22:01,148 --> 00:22:02,400
Thank you.

302
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:04,156
You're welcome.

303
00:22:15,340 --> 00:22:16,996
Good!

304
00:22:18,800 --> 00:22:21,700
Mr. Luo, you're really good at it!

305
00:22:21,700 --> 00:22:22,960
Thank you, Chairman Fang.

306
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:25,084
- Please. 
 - Okay.

307
00:22:25,084 --> 00:22:26,960
Is it your first time coming here?

308
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:28,416
Yes.

309
00:22:28,416 --> 00:22:32,700
The environment here is nice, and the golf course was built to international standards.

310
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:35,860
People my age should practice more.

311
00:22:35,860 --> 00:22:37,680
Sounds reasonable.

312
00:23:51,860 --> 00:23:55,300
An earthquake! An earthquake!

313
00:23:55,300 --> 00:23:58,496
Everyone, come out of the rooms!

314
00:23:58,496 --> 00:24:01,120
- Run! 
