315
00:24:01,120 --> 00:24:03,350
An earthquake!

316
00:24:04,136 --> 00:24:06,732
Hurry up!

317
00:24:08,060 --> 00:24:09,660
Hurry!

318
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:21,496
Come on!

319
00:24:21,496 --> 00:24:23,272
Speed up!

320
00:24:26,180 --> 00:24:27,836
 This way!

321
00:24:29,340 --> 00:24:32,904
Hurry and run! It's an earthquake!

322
00:24:34,520 --> 00:24:37,560
Go to the playground now!

323
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:51,060
Mom...

324
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:59,596
Run!

