00:25:16,070 --> 00:25:18,600
 An earthquake!

330
00:25:42,080 --> 00:25:44,120
 According to the National Seismic Network,

331
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:46,620
 an earthquake with a magnitude of 6

332
00:25:46,620 --> 00:25:48,860
 happened in Fengxi at 10:28 Beijing time.

333
00:25:48,860 --> 00:25:52,000
 The epicenter distance from the provincial capital city is about 60 kilometers.

334
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:54,100
