335
00:25:54,100 --> 00:25:58,120
 It's a shallow earthquake this time with high damage levels.

336
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:59,660
 The losses caused by the quake are serious.

337
00:25:59,660 --> 00:26:01,820
 Casualties are currently being counted.

338
00:26:01,820 --> 00:26:04,020
 The leadership of the Party and the State

339
00:26:04,020 --> 00:26:07,000
 are attaching great importance to the quake, and have commanded the PLA and PAP

340
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:09,780
 to work together to provide disaster relief quickly.

341
00:26:09,780 --> 00:26:11,880
 China Earthquake Administration has dispatched

342
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:15,440
 emergency response teams and work teams,

343
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:19,800
 216 people in total, to provide emergency rescue and service on the site.

344
00:26:19,800 --> 00:26:23,300
 Red Cross Society of China has allocated 557 tents, 2500 blankets,

345
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:25,880
 and other disaster-relief materials into the county.

346
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:29,580
 National Health Commission has assigned more than 10 health emergency teams...

347
00:26:29,580 --> 00:26:32,080
- Peng! 
  - to the disaster area.

348
00:26:32,080 --> 00:26:34,692
Take it and take care.

349
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:38,540
 Our hospital party committee has considered

350
00:26:38,540 --> 00:26:41,840
 and decided to dispatch medical teams to support the site.

351
00:26:41,840 --> 00:26:46,880
 Zhan Yan will lead the first set and Cai Yuxiao will lead the second.

352
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:50,316
 President, I apply to join group one.

353
00:26:50,316 --> 00:26:51,800
 Dr. Zhan is a lady.

354
00:26:51,800 --> 00:26:53,520
