00:26:59,380 --> 00:27:02,364
 I won't let you down.

358
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:06,800

359
00:27:06,800 --> 00:27:09,460
Director Liu! I'm Qingshan.

360
00:27:09,460 --> 00:27:11,540
The Light Chaser Rescue Team is ready.

361
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:13,540
We apply to rescue Fengxi.

362
00:27:13,540 --> 00:27:16,760
 I agree. Remember to obey commands.

363
00:27:16,760 --> 00:27:20,260
All the rescue teams are rushing to Fengxi.

364
00:27:20,260 --> 00:27:24,520
- Unified dispatch is necessary to ensure rescue efforts
go smoothly and orderly. 
 -  Roger.

365
00:27:24,520 --> 00:27:26,240
 I'm on the way there.

366
00:27:26,240 --> 00:27:28,260
Call me as you get something new.

367
00:27:28,260 --> 00:27:29,760
Yes.

368
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:34,736
- Let's go. 
