369
00:27:44,750 --> 00:27:47,630

370
00:27:48,940 --> 00:27:51,970

371
00:27:55,080 --> 00:27:56,400
What's happening?

372
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,840
I can't contact Luo Yuan.

373
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:59,200
I have to find her.

374
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:01,060
