375
00:28:01,060 --> 00:28:02,140
Please look after her!

376
00:28:02,140 --> 00:28:03,944
Okay!

377
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:14,520
 Fengxi Fire Fighting Force rushed to the disaster area.

378
00:28:14,520 --> 00:28:17,920
 They were the first batch of professionals to appear on the scene.

379
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:22,100
 The Air Force has dispatched large and medium-sized military and civilian transport aircraft

380
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:27,224
 to transport PLA soldiers and armed police officers and soldiers to the Fengqi disaster area by air in batches.

381
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:40,744
Please come and help my dad!

382
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:53,440
Excuse me, how can I get to Fengxi School of Special Education?

383
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:55,200
They are still inside, but don't go any further.

384
00:28:55,200 --> 00:28:57,480
Aftershocks keep coming, it's too dangerous.

385
00:29:39,380 --> 00:29:41,080
 Let's go!

386
00:29:41,080 --> 00:29:45,500
 Mom! Mom...

387
00:29:47,380 --> 00:29:49,792
 Mom!

388
00:29:52,780 --> 00:29:55,292
 - Mom...  
 - Anyone here?

389
00:29:56,340 --> 00:29:57,940
 Mom...

390
00:29:59,140 --> 00:30:01,040
 Mom...

391
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:11,160
Kid! Can you hear me?

392
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:13,100
 Mom...

393
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:19,140
Kid! Hang in there!

394
00:30:19,140 --> 00:30:21,344
I'll come and save you!

395
00:30:27,340 --> 00:30:29,450

396
00:31:13,360 --> 00:31:15,068
 Be careful!

397
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:16,840
 Let's go!

398
00:31:16,840 --> 00:31:18,540
 Slow down.

399
00:31:19,860 --> 00:31:22,112
 Watch out!

400
00:31:50,660 --> 00:31:52,668
Captain! Captain!

401
00:31:52,668 --> 00:31:55,148
Captain!

402
00:31:55,148 --> 00:31:56,760
Tell everyone to speed up.

403
00:31:56,800 --> 00:31:59,500
- We need to get there ASAP! 
 - Okay!

404
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:19,408
Kid!

405
00:32:19,408 --> 00:32:22,160
Kid! Hold on!

406
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:23,740
I can't save you only by myself.

407
00:32:23,740 --> 00:32:26,492
I need to find others.

408
00:32:26,492 --> 00:32:31,144
Don't leave me... Don't leave me alone. I'm scared.

409
00:32:31,900 --> 00:32:33,800
I'll be right back! Hang in there!

410
00:32:37,420 --> 00:32:38,972
Anyone here?

411
00:32:38,972 --> 00:32:40,880
Who can hear me?

412
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:44,200
A kid is here! Come and save him!

413
00:32:53,560 --> 00:32:56,660
Kid? Kid!

414
00:33:02,140 --> 00:33:04,700
 Materials are here.

415
00:33:04,700 --> 00:33:07,120
Hurry up!

416
00:33:20,140 --> 00:33:21,840
 Doctor.

417
00:33:21,840 --> 00:33:23,800
Please be gentle.

418
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:26,420
 Doctor!

419
00:33:26,420 --> 00:33:29,100
Come and check on him. Hurry!

420
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:31,500
- No thanks now. 
 - Confirm the blood transfusion location.

421
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:33,660
- Zirui, prepare for surgery. 
 - Sis!

422
00:33:33,660 --> 00:33:34,620
Sis!

423
00:33:34,620 --> 00:33:35,520
Why are you here?

424
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:38,892
I was here to take a walk.

425
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,180
What's wrong with your hand?

426
00:33:41,180 --> 00:33:44,600
It's because I was in a hurry to escape and then I fell down.

427
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:46,320
Find a nurse to patch it up.

428
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:48,680
Go back with the hospital transport vehicle.

429
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:51,740
Don't bring others trouble. I need to get to a surgery.

430
00:33:51,740 --> 00:33:54,964
Don't leave me alone...

431
00:34:02,100 --> 00:34:03,600
Kid?

432
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:06,444
Can you hear me?

433
00:34:06,444 --> 00:34:08,000
Kid?

434
00:34:13,720 --> 00:34:15,220
Kid!

435
00:34:15,220 --> 00:34:18,504
Can you chat with me?

436
00:34:19,380 --> 00:34:21,116
What's your name?

437
00:34:21,116 --> 00:34:23,520
My name is Lele.

438
00:34:23,520 --> 00:34:25,020
Lele.

439
00:34:25,020 --> 00:34:27,116
Good boy.

440
00:34:27,116 --> 00:34:29,760
Is anyone else beside you?

441
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:31,452
My mom...

442
00:34:31,452 --> 00:34:33,000
She's here...

443
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:34,844
Can she talk?

444
00:34:34,844 --> 00:34:38,172
She's sleeping.

445
00:34:41,580 --> 00:34:45,736
Lele, she's exhausted.

446
00:34:45,736 --> 00:34:48,332
Let her sleep for a while.

447
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:55,900
Lele, don't cry.

448
00:34:59,980 --> 00:35:04,176
Let me tell you a story, okay?

449
00:35:16,100 --> 00:35:18,252
Lele.

450
00:35:18,252 --> 00:35:23,180
There was a little boy at your age.

451
00:35:23,180 --> 00:35:24,780
He's the same as you,

452
00:35:24,780 --> 00:35:30,530
suffering from a serious earthquake in his childhood.

453
00:35:31,368 --> 00:35:35,960
He and his parents...

454
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:38,912
were buried beneath a collapsed house.

455
00:35:38,912 --> 00:35:41,256
It was dark all around.

456
00:35:41,256 --> 00:35:43,292
He could see nothing.

457
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:46,412
He was quite scared...

458
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:51,636
so he kept crying.

459
00:36:01,140 --> 00:36:04,716
 Mom... I'm frightened...

460
00:36:04,716 --> 00:36:08,960
 Calm down, my son. Mom is here.

461
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:12,780
 Don't worry. Someone is on the way to save us.

462
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:14,400
 Don't be afraid.

463
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:17,100
 Can they find us?

464
00:36:17,100 --> 00:36:18,900
 Yes.

465
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:20,660
 I'm sure they will.

466
00:36:23,860 --> 00:36:26,228
But he didn't give up.

467
00:36:26,228 --> 00:36:29,828
Lele, he was finally rescued later on.

468
00:36:29,828 --> 00:36:34,320
He survived and he had a younger sister.

469
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:37,368
He had a happy life.

470
00:36:37,368 --> 00:36:39,196
So...

471
00:36:39,196 --> 00:36:41,312
So trust me.

472
00:36:41,312 --> 00:36:42,840
Don't give up!

473
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:44,728
You must hang in there.

474
00:36:44,728 --> 00:36:47,084
You will be saved.

475
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:51,576
Yuan Yuan.

476
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:54,468
Yuan Yuan.

477
00:36:59,650 --> 00:37:01,590

478
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:14,844
Lele.

479
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:19,880
Lele? Lele?

480
00:37:20,740 --> 00:37:22,836
Don't fall asleep!

481
00:37:22,836 --> 00:37:24,500
Lele?

482
00:37:28,380 --> 00:37:31,756
Lele! Wake up, Lele!

483
00:37:50,580 --> 00:37:52,912
Wait!

484
00:37:52,912 --> 00:37:54,200
A kid is here!

485
00:37:54,200 --> 00:37:56,040
Stop! What's going on inside?

486
00:37:56,040 --> 00:37:57,460
He's called Lele.

487
00:37:57,460 --> 00:37:59,160
I was talking with him.

488
00:37:59,160 --> 00:38:00,520
But he has no response now.

489
00:38:00,520 --> 00:38:01,520
I'm afraid he can't wait.

