00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:44,080
- Peng, forcible entry. 
 - Yes.

503
00:38:44,080 --> 00:38:47,280
Falcon, lead others there at once.

504
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,640
We'll join you soon.

505
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,640
Roger.

