00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:59,612
Lele! Hang in there!

509
00:39:04,420 --> 00:39:06,572
 Step aside!

510
00:39:13,120 --> 00:39:15,060
The bleeding has stopped.

511
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:18,340
Sew it up and I'll go to the next one.

512
00:39:18,340 --> 00:39:19,940
Okay.

513
00:40:17,680 --> 00:40:20,560
Peng, send him to a hospital nearby.

514
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:21,880
Yes.

