00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:23,080
Wukong!

516
00:40:23,080 --> 00:40:25,480
Excuse me!

517
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,820
Sir.

518
00:40:26,820 --> 00:40:28,700
You'd better leave here at once. It's risky.

519
00:40:28,700 --> 00:40:32,380
Others! Let's go and join the rest.

